	<description>
		<![CDATA[
			<div class="overview-header">
			<h2>
			  <small style="display: block;">Responsive news & magazine Joomla template for Joomla 2.5. and Joomla 3 - <strong>JA Teline IV</strong>.</small>
			</h2>
			<p><strong>JA Teline IV</strong> is the latest of the Teline Series of Joomla! News site templates.</p>
			<p>Teline templates are very popular with our users, however teline templates at times can require careful devlopment to get the desired results.</p>
			<p>New users are advised to install quickstart on localhost for reference and to follow userguide for settings. Best results are achieved by using 
			the demo default settings and then tweaking them to suit the user requirement.</p>
			<p><i><strong>Note:</strong> JA Teline IV is support RTL language.</i></p>
		  </div>
				]]>
	</description>
